<HEADLINE>
FT  17 JUN 94 / FT Guide to World Cup Football (13): The route to the final
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
 ----------------------------------------------------------------------
                               FIRST ROUND
 ----------------------------------------------------------------------
Teams from the 24 qualifying countries are divided into six groups
(A-F). Each team plays its three group opponents once; the first two in
each group plus the four third-placed teams with the best records
proceed to the Second Round. Games played June 17 to June 30 at San
Francisco, Los Angeles, Detroit, Chicago, Boston, Dallas, New York,
Washington and Orlando.
 ----------------------------------------------------------------------
                            SECOND ROUND
 ----------------------------------------------------------------------
                         July 2, Chicago
                Winners Group C vs Third place team
                        July 2, Washington
                  Second Group C vs Second Group A
                        July 3, Los Angeles
                Winners Group A vs Third place team
                           July 3, Dallas
                   Second Group F vs Second Group B
                        July 4, San Francisco
                Winners Group B vs Third place team
                           July 4, Orlando
                 Winners Group F vs Second Group E
                           July 5, Boston
               Winners Group D vs Third place team
                           July 5, New York
                Winners Group E vs Second Group D
 ----------------------------------------------------------------------
                            QUARTER FINALS
 ----------------------------------------------------------------------
                            July 9, Boston
              Winners at Boston vs winners at Washington
                           July 9, Dallas
            Winners at Orlando vs winners at San Francisco
                      July 10, San Francisco
              Winners at Los Angeles vs winners at Dallas
                        July 10, New York
             Winners at New York vs winners at Chicago
 ----------------------------------------------------------------------
                             SEMI FINALS
 ----------------------------------------------------------------------
                          July 13, Los Angeles
            Winners at San Francisco vs winners at Dallas
                          July 13, New York
               Winners at New York vs winners at Boston
 ----------------------------------------------------------------------
                           THIRD-PLACE MATCH
 ----------------------------------------------------------------------
                         July 16, Los Angeles
              Losers at Los Angeles vs losers at New York
 ----------------------------------------------------------------------
                              THE FINAL
 ----------------------------------------------------------------------
                        July 17, Los Angeles
            Winners at Los Angeles vs winners at New York
 ----------------------------------------------------------------------
</TEXT>
